  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Our Discord!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/fce1987e026047bd537a82f34fca9e06.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/fce1987e026047bd537a82f34fca9e06.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/fce1987e026047bd537a82f34fca9e06.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/4ca7a6f4c9fda2b10d4a435e9bd1c647.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=600 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/4ca7a6f4c9fda2b10d4a435e9bd1c647.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/4ca7a6f4c9fda2b10d4a435e9bd1c647.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/ffe3f68def9bfe6ff237cee723bc4de0.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/ffe3f68def9bfe6ff237cee723bc4de0.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/ffe3f68def9bfe6ff237cee723bc4de0.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experience an engaging story filled with charm, adventure and cute animals!<br></li><li>Explore a large, hand drawn world full of colorful characters!<br></li><li>Craft creative solutions by combining items with the new Toolbelt!<br></li><li>Solve challenging brainteasers and navigate intricate puzzle-dungeons!<br></li><li>Tailor your experience with new guidance and hint systems!<br></li><li>Orient yourself and fast-travel with the new map systems!<br></li><li>Collect coins and recruit characters for bonus artwork, figurines and lore!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Second Chapter of NAIRI</h2>After the events of <i>NAIRI: Tower of Shirin</i>, Nairi continues on her quest to save her family. While she and her companions try to overcome the many dangers of the corrupt city of Shirin, an apocalyptic prophecy threatens to devour everything.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/eb300f9f04425475c47828b1ed5ccb3c.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/eb300f9f04425475c47828b1ed5ccb3c.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/eb300f9f04425475c47828b1ed5ccb3c.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/e5147e470740b01bb7ebc1aa7248f5e9.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/e5147e470740b01bb7ebc1aa7248f5e9.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/e5147e470740b01bb7ebc1aa7248f5e9.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore, Collect & Craft</h2>Explore the oasis city of Shirin to meet cute, wacky and even dangerous characters!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/cdcf02b9a7e459fbe4c45f735541b58e.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/cdcf02b9a7e459fbe4c45f735541b58e.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/cdcf02b9a7e459fbe4c45f735541b58e.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Find items and combine them in interesting ways!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/872c5f7e932c78e3514580110b2cda9a.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/872c5f7e932c78e3514580110b2cda9a.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/872c5f7e932c78e3514580110b2cda9a.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenging Puzzles</h2>Solve your way through the many puzzles of Shirin!<br>You may even encounter a 'puzzle-dungeon' - a complex space filled with interconnected puzzles which will pose a true challenge.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/8cef46a0ad0e81320e00574030e7ff91.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/8cef46a0ad0e81320e00574030e7ff91.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/8cef46a0ad0e81320e00574030e7ff91.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/19cbfab9950a0b79eb55e6f76b7f6fb9.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/19cbfab9950a0b79eb55e6f76b7f6fb9.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/19cbfab9950a0b79eb55e6f76b7f6fb9.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Cutest Hint System</h2>Spend coins on hints ranging from nudges to complete solutions.<br>And if you're just here for the story, you may even skip entire puzzle-dungeons!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/4130feacbe45a799db795f27ff4ee265.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/4130feacbe45a799db795f27ff4ee265.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/4130feacbe45a799db795f27ff4ee265.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Maps & Fast-Travel</h2>Not sure where you are or where to go? Use the map!<br>Be sure to use fast-travel if you don't feel like backtracking.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/fd4d6ca476b76ded01f15fb479708a1a.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/fd4d6ca476b76ded01f15fb479708a1a.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/fd4d6ca476b76ded01f15fb479708a1a.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/061a5b6349f65805fd0d340f6507e12e.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/061a5b6349f65805fd0d340f6507e12e.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/061a5b6349f65805fd0d340f6507e12e.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collectibles!</h2>Collect coins, recruit characters, find hidden concept art and purchase figurines for extra lore!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/1ad068bdf48d235aabe08a2b5c3e88d0.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/1ad068bdf48d235aabe08a2b5c3e88d0.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/1ad068bdf48d235aabe08a2b5c3e88d0.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/ba3a5adae528031e455c3434cd102945.poster.avif?t=1740571304\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/ba3a5adae528031e455c3434cd102945.webm?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225200/extras/ba3a5adae528031e455c3434cd102945.mp4?t=1740571304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
